**Scenario: USMCA Suspension / Emergency Renegotiation**

**Trigger Events:**
- U.S. Congress: USMCA Article 34.6 review triggered
  - Rationale: "Systemic corruption = breach of agreement integrity provisions"
  - 60% House + Senate vote threshold EASILY met (bipartisan corruption opposition)
- Section 232 tariffs reinstated: "National security" concerns (corrupt neighbor = security risk)
- Buy American provisions: Canadian firms excluded (integrity questions)
- Border security overhaul: Every shipment inspected (chaos at crossings)

