4. **Reserve depletion:** Bank of Canada burns through $106B trying to defend CAD
5. **Speculative attack:** Currency traders short CAD (George Soros-style)

**Devaluation Calculation:**

**Historical Precedents:**
- **Turkish lira:** Corruption + authoritarianism → -45% in 2 years (2018-2020)
