- Database overhaul: Case management, audit trails = $1-2B
- Cybersecurity: Prevent tampering = $500M-1B

**Personnel Costs ($5-10 billion):**
- New hires (oversight): 2,000 positions × $150K = $300M/year × 5 years = $1.5B
- Terminations (corrupt agents): 500-1,000 severance/legal = $500M-1B
- Whistleblower protection: Office + hotline = $100M/year × 5 years = $500M
- Victim compensation unit: $1-2B

**Opportunity Cost ($20-40 billion):**
